graph LR
    subgraph "Red Hat OpenShift AI 3.3 Platform"
        RHODSOp[RHODS Operator<br/>v1.6.0-5550<br/>Central Control Plane]

        subgraph "Component Operators"
            KServe[KServe Operator<br/>v0.15]
            ModelCtrl[odh-model-controller<br/>v1.27.0-1157]
            DSP[Data Science Pipelines<br/>Operator v0.0.1]
            ModelReg[Model Registry<br/>Operator 4fdd8de]
            NBCtrl[ODH Notebook<br/>Controller v1.27.0-1417]
            Training[Training Operator<br/>v1.9.0]
            Trainer[Kubeflow Trainer<br/>v2.1.0]
            Ray[KubeRay Operator<br/>v1.4.2]
            Feast[Feast Operator<br/>98a224e7c]
            MLflow[MLflow Operator<br/>49b5d8d]
            Llama[Llama Stack Operator<br/>v0.6.0]
            TrustyAI[TrustyAI Operator<br/>v1.39.0]
        end

        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard<br/>v1.21.0-18<br/>React UI]
    end

    subgraph "External OpenShift/K8s Dependencies"
        Istio[Istio Service Mesh<br/>1.20+<br/>VirtualServices, mTLS]
        Knative[Knative Serving<br/>1.12+<br/>Autoscaling]
        CertMgr[cert-manager<br/>1.13+<br/>TLS Certificates]
        GatewayAPI[Gateway API<br/>HTTPRoutes]
        OAuth[OpenShift OAuth<br/>Authentication]
        K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server<br/>Resource Management]
        ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA<br/>TLS Certificate Generation]
        Prometheus[Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection]
    end

    subgraph "External Services"
        S3[S3-Compatible Storage<br/>Model/Artifact Storage]
        PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL<br/>Metadata Persistence]
        MySQL[MySQL/MariaDB<br/>Pipeline Metadata]
        Redis[Redis<br/>Feature Caching]
        HuggingFace[HuggingFace Hub<br/>Model/Dataset Downloads]
        NGC[NVIDIA NGC API<br/>NIM Accounts]
        Argo[Argo Workflows<br/>Pipeline Execution]
        Volcano[Volcano/Coscheduling<br/>Gang Scheduling]
        JobSet[JobSet<br/>Multi-node Training]
        Kueue[Kueue<br/>Job Queueing]
    end

    subgraph "Integration Patterns"
        CRD[CRD-Based Integration<br/>Watch/Reconcile]
        API[API Call Integration<br/>REST/gRPC]
        SharedInfra[Shared Infrastructure<br/>Routes, Metrics, TLS]
        Storage[Storage Integration<br/>S3, PostgreSQL, PVCs]
    end

    %% Central Operator Relationships
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Dashboard
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| KServe
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| DSP
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| ModelReg
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| NBCtrl
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Training
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Trainer
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Ray
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Feast
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| MLflow
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| Llama
    RHODSOp -->|deploys| TrustyAI

    %% Component Dependencies on External OpenShift/K8s
    KServe -->|traffic mgmt| Istio
    KServe -->|autoscaling| Knative
    KServe -->|certificates| CertMgr
    KServe -->|uses| K8sAPI

    ModelCtrl -->|extends KServe| KServe
    ModelCtrl -->|creates Routes| GatewayAPI
    ModelCtrl -->|creates HTTPRoutes| GatewayAPI
    ModelCtrl -->|uses| K8sAPI

    DSP -->|pipeline execution| Argo
    DSP -->|uses| K8sAPI

    NBCtrl -->|creates HTTPRoutes| GatewayAPI
    NBCtrl -->|uses| K8sAPI

    MLflow -->|creates HTTPRoutes| GatewayAPI
    MLflow -->|uses| K8sAPI

    Training -->|gang scheduling| Volcano
    Training -->|job queueing| Kueue
    Training -->|uses| K8sAPI

    Trainer -->|multi-node jobs| JobSet
    Trainer -->|gang scheduling| Volcano
    Trainer -->|uses| K8sAPI

    Ray -->|certificates| CertMgr
    Ray -->|uses| GatewayAPI
    Ray -->|uses| K8sAPI

    TrustyAI -->|patches InferenceServices| KServe
    TrustyAI -->|traffic splitting| Istio
    TrustyAI -->|job queueing| Kueue
    TrustyAI -->|uses| K8sAPI

    %% Dashboard Integration
    Dashboard -->|authenticates via| OAuth
    Dashboard -->|reads CRs| K8sAPI
    Dashboard -->|creates Notebooks| NBCtrl
    Dashboard -->|creates InferenceServices| KServe
    Dashboard -->|creates ModelRegistries| ModelReg
    Dashboard -->|queries metrics| Prometheus

    %% All Components use Shared Infrastructure
    RHODSOp -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    KServe -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    ModelCtrl -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    DSP -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    ModelReg -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    NBCtrl -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    Training -.->|uses| ServiceCA
    Dashboard -.->|uses| ServiceCA

    RHODSOp -.->|exports metrics| Prometheus
    KServe -.->|exports metrics| Prometheus
    ModelCtrl -.->|exports metrics| Prometheus
    DSP -.->|exports metrics| Prometheus

    %% External Service Dependencies
    KServe -->|model downloads| S3
    DSP -->|artifact storage| S3
    DSP -->|metadata| MySQL
    Training -->|checkpoints| S3
    Trainer -->|datasets| S3
    Trainer -->|model downloads| HuggingFace

    ModelReg -->|metadata storage| PostgreSQL
    MLflow -->|experiment tracking| PostgreSQL
    MLflow -->|artifact storage| S3
    Feast -->|feature metadata| PostgreSQL
    Feast -->|offline features| S3
    Feast -->|online cache| Redis
    TrustyAI -->|inference logs| PostgreSQL

    ModelCtrl -->|NIM validation| NGC

    %% Integration Points (Component-to-Component)
    DSP -.->|deploys models| KServe
    DSP -.->|registers metadata| ModelReg
    NBCtrl -.->|pipeline secrets| DSP
    Feast -.->|ConfigMap injection| NBCtrl

